{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter03_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "这房间里的东西也太可疑了，要我说你就是凶手把",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我之前是设计师，对精巧的东西有浓郁的兴趣，总不能因为这点就断定我是凶手把",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "即使这么说可所有不利的证据还是指向你，光这点你就很难洗脱嫌疑",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_5",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "哦？可我觉得酗酒伤人在动机上更合理哦",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "动机...的确作案需要动机，大家昨天跟C在一块儿时干了什么？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_7",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "撕...我记得他是说要送我一瓶酒来着？但最后好像不了了之了。",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "晚上C与往常一样来我房间里向我传教，我对他的教义不感兴趣，他自己说完就走了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（说谎）我在白天倒是见过他，口里神神叨叨的晚上喝醉后就不得而知了。",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "总感觉有些话语与之前自相矛盾...",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_11",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|branch_a_start",
                "B|branch_b_start"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "天下没有免费的午餐，你还说不了了之？不不不，证据就是：",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_12",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "酒瓶",
                "branch_a_success",
                "branch_a_fail"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_success",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "就是你房间里的那瓶酒，况且也不是白送的把，我不信一个酒鬼还有收集卷轴的习惯",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "可这...又说明什么呢？我咬死是我不记得了你又怎么办？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "愚蠢，都到了这一地步了还敢装傻充楞吗",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_15",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "说明酒是你自己拿的，因为C没有兑现他的承诺于是你擅自闯入了C的房间。",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "等..等等......",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "胜负已分，你的说辞站不住脚",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_18",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["A", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_19",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_fail",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "这点....能证明",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_20",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "果然当初就该把你往死里打！",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "赶紧投票把，浪费时间",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_22",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_23",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你隐瞒了事实真相，这点就是",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_24",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "黑皮书",
                "branch_b_success_1",
                "branch_b_fail_1"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_success_1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你说你一直在看书，那这本与众不同的书该怎么解释",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_25",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我有什么需要解释的？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_26",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你不是对宗教无感吗，怎么会看这种书？看位置恐怕是昨天才看，或是昨天某人才给你？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_27",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "呃！！！也有可能只是我没发现这本书，谁知道C什么时候留下来的",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "不，唯独你不会犯这种错误",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_29",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "RequireEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "羊皮纸卷",
                "branch_b_success_2",
                "branch_b_fail_2"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_success_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你强大的控制欲不会允许这种错误\n你并非没理C反而达成了与A和C同样的锲约关系，这样一来，你也有了去C房间的理由",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "呵呵，确实如你所说，但我去只是寒暄。为了避嫌我只好撒谎说没理C",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_31",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["B", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_32_b_end",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_fail_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "对！就是这个",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_33",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这根本说明不了任何问题，请你深思熟虑后再发言好吗",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_34",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_35",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_fail_1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "对！就是这个",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_36",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "这根本说明不了任何问题，请你深思熟虑后再发言好吗",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_37",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_38",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "trial_end",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "记录完成，下一轮。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_40_load",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadScene"
        }
    ]
}